The paper deals with online algorithms and their performance under stochastic input models. This topic is closely related to game theory (cs.GT) as well as data structures (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information theory (cs.IT), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely candidates for this paper.
